/// Shared hk preset for risu729 projects.
/// Consumers: `amends "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/risu729/hk-config/<version>/presets.pkl"`
/// then set `hooks = helpers.standardHooks(helpers.pick(...))` in `hk.pkl`.
amends "package://github.com/jdx/hk/releases/download/v1.53.0/hk@1.53.0#/Config.pkl"

min_hk_version = "1.53.0"
